Xin chào ?

00:14:21.502 --> 00:14:25.003
Còn ai ở ngoài đó không ?
còn ai sống sót không ?

00:14:26.507 --> 00:14:30.843
Chúng tôi còn sống này, gần như thế.

00:14:30.845 --> 00:14:34.680
Tận thế khiến tôi buồn quá.

00:14:34.682 --> 00:14:36.849
Hãy cho tôi 1 tín hiệu nếu bạn
nghe được giai điệu này.

00:14:36.851 --> 00:14:41.687
♪ I saw boys, toys,
electric irons, and TVs... ♪

00:14:43.991 --> 00:14:46.441
Có ai ở đó không ?

00:14:46.443 --> 00:14:49.778
Có ai không ?

00:14:49.780 --> 00:14:52.698
Bạn sẽ khó mà quên được bài hát này đấy.

00:14:54.535 --> 00:14:56.785
